Component is:
    - reusable building blocks in user interfaces
    - combination of HTML code, css and Javascript code for same logic

Concepts:
    - re-usability
    - separation (one responsibility for one component)
    - reactivity
    - declarative approach (define the target state and let React figure out the actual Javascript DOM instructions)
    - custom HTML element

Component consists of:
    - HTML
    - CSS
    - JavaScript
